{
  "texts": [
    "Let us consider the Fermat potential or arrival time from Eq.",
    "(34), that is",
    "plus the constant 1 2 |β| 2, which can be discarded.",
    "It is interesting and useful to visualize τ (θ, β) as a surface: the time-delay or arrival-time surface.",
    "Without a lens, the arrival-time surface looks like a parabolic well with a minimum at θ = β."
  ]
}